CustomField.description: The API name, including namespace, of the field on the Project object you want to use as the total revenue for fixed fee projects. If left blank, the value in the Bookings field is used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name, including namespace, of the field on the Project object you want to use as the total revenue for fixed fee projects. If left blank, the value in the Bookings field is used.
CustomField.label: Total Revenue Field on Project
